data.description: I invite you to come set your eyes on this gorgeous 4 bedroom home with 2 bathrooms and a 2 car garage that's located on a beautiful corner lot. Relax in the backyard that has been freshly sodded and features a fun filled family 16X32 ft above ground pool. From the kitchen enjoy the panoramic view of the pool. Access the backyard with either the 2 pool bath doors or the stackable slider. Home boasts with upgrades, to name a few, tray ceilings, soft touch cabinets, recessed lighting, gutters, granite countertops, petrified indonesian wood in master bathroom shower and more. Outside of the home don't forget to stop and smell the roses in the breath taking landscape. New interior paint, vinyl fencing, irrigation, hand scraped hardwood floors, upgraded carpet in 3 bedrooms. The fourth bedroom can also be used as a den/office and features french doors. The listing agent is the owner of the home. Parade Of Homes Winner this Weitlund built open floor plan home has a deep soaking tub, soaker sink in laundry room, master bedroom with bay window, frosted double pane front doors and a accent wall in one of the bedrooms.
